010@HistoryLogProps(
011    opCode = 256,
012    displayName = "Dexcom G6 CGM Data",
013    usedByAndroid = true,
014    usedByTidepool = true, // LID_CGM_DATA_GXB
015    usedByTconnectsync = true
016)
017public class DexcomG6CGMHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
018    
019    private int glucoseValueStatusRaw;
020    private GlucoseValueStatus glucoseValueStatus;
021    private int cgmDataTypeRaw;
022    private Set<CgmDataType> cgmDataTypes;
023    private int rate;
024    private int algorithmState;
025    private int rssi;
026    private int currentGlucoseDisplayValue;
027    private long timeStampSeconds;
028    private int egvInfoBitmaskRaw;
029    private Set<EgvInfo> egvInfo;
030    private int interval;
031    
032    public DexcomG6CGMHistoryLog() {}
033    
034    public DexcomG6CGMHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int glucoseValueStatusRaw, int cgmDataTypeRaw, int rate, int algorithmState, int rssi, int currentGlucoseDisplayValue, long timeStampSeconds, int egvInfoBitmask, int interval) {
035        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, glucoseValueStatusRaw, cgmDataTypeRaw, rate, algorithmState, rssi, currentGlucoseDisplayValue, timeStampSeconds, egvInfoBitmask, interval);
036        parse(cargo);
037        
038    }
039
040    public int typeId() {
041        return 256;
042    }

044/**
045     * TODO: this needs to be checked against the tconnectsync eventparser code since they seem to differ     *     * <br>     *     * <table border="1">
046     * <caption>Parsed fields for DexcomG6CGMHistoryLog:</caption>
047     * <tr><td><code>glucoseValueStatusRaw</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
048     * <tr><td><code>glucoseValueStatus</code></td><td><code>getGlucoseValueStatus()</code></td></tr>
049     * <tr><td><code>cgmDataTypeRaw</code></td><td><code>raw[12]</code></td></tr>
050     * <tr><td><code>cgmDataTypes</code></td><td><code>getCgmDataTypes()</code></td></tr>
051     * <tr><td><code>rate</code></td><td><code>raw[13]</code></td></tr>
052     * <tr><td><code>algorithmState</code></td><td><code>raw[14]</code></td></tr>
053     * <tr><td><code>rssi</code></td><td><code>raw[15]</code></td></tr>
054     * <tr><td><code>currentGlucoseDisplayValue</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 16)</code></td></tr>
055     * <tr><td><code>timeStampSeconds</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
056     * <tr><td><code>egvInfoBitmaskRaw</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 22)</code></td></tr>
057     * <tr><td><code>egvInfo</code></td><td><code>getEgvInfo()</code></td></tr>
058     * <tr><td><code>interval</code></td><td><code>raw[24]</code></td></tr>
059     * </table>
060     */
061    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
062        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
063        this.cargo = raw;
064        parseBase(raw);
065        this.glucoseValueStatusRaw = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
066        this.glucoseValueStatus = getGlucoseValueStatus();
067        this.cgmDataTypeRaw = raw[12];
068        this.cgmDataTypes = getCgmDataTypes();
069        this.rate = raw[13];
070        this.algorithmState = raw[14];
071        this.rssi = raw[15];
072        this.currentGlucoseDisplayValue = Bytes.readShort(raw, 16);
073        this.timeStampSeconds = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18);
074        this.egvInfoBitmaskRaw = Bytes.readShort(raw, 22);
075        this.egvInfo = getEgvInfo();
076        this.interval = raw[24];
077        
078    }

082     * <table border="1">
083     * <caption>Byte layout for DexcomG6CGMHistoryLog.buildCargo(...):</caption>
084     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>
085     * <tr><td>0</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
086     * <tr><td>1</td><td><code>new byte[]{1} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
087     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
088     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
089     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
090     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
091     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
092     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
093     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
094     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
095     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(glucoseValueStatus) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
096     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(glucoseValueStatus) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
097     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>(byte) cgmDataType</code></td></tr>
098     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>(byte) rate</code></td></tr>
099     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>(byte) algorithmState</code></td></tr>
100     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>(byte) rssi</code></td></tr>
101     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(currentGlucoseDisplayValue) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
102     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(currentGlucoseDisplayValue) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
103     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>toUint32(timeStampSeconds) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
104     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>toUint32(timeStampSeconds) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
105     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>toUint32(timeStampSeconds) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
106     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>toUint32(timeStampSeconds) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
107     * <tr><td>22</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(egvInfoBitmask) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
108     * <tr><td>23</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(egvInfoBitmask) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
109     * <tr><td>24</td><td><code>(byte) interval</code></td></tr>
110     * <tr><td>25</td><td><code>(byte) (1)</code></td></tr>
111     * </table>
112     */
113    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int glucoseValueStatus, int cgmDataType, int rate, int algorithmState, int rssi, int currentGlucoseDisplayValue, long timeStampSeconds, int egvInfoBitmask, int interval) {
114        return Bytes.combine(
115            new byte[]{0, 1},
116            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
117            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
118            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(glucoseValueStatus), 
119            new byte[]{ (byte) cgmDataType }, 
120            new byte[]{ (byte) rate }, 
121            new byte[]{ (byte) algorithmState }, 
122            new byte[]{ (byte) rssi }, 
123            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(currentGlucoseDisplayValue), 
124            Bytes.toUint32(timeStampSeconds), 
125            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(egvInfoBitmask), 
126            new byte[]{ (byte) interval },
127            new byte[]{ 1 }); // missing param?
128    }

134    public enum GlucoseValueStatus {
135        NORMAL(0),
136        HIGH(1),
137        LOW(2)
138
139        ;
140        private int id;
141        GlucoseValueStatus(int id) {
142            this.id = id;
143        }
144
145        public static GlucoseValueStatus fromId(int id) {
146            for (GlucoseValueStatus r : values()) {
147                if (r.id == id) {
148                    return r;
149                }
150            }
151            return null;
152        }
153
154        public int getId() {
155            return id;
156        }
157    }
158
159    public GlucoseValueStatus getGlucoseValueStatus() {
160        return GlucoseValueStatus.fromId(glucoseValueStatusRaw);
161    }
162
163    public int getCgmDataTypeRaw() {
164        return cgmDataTypeRaw;
165    }

167    public enum CgmDataType {
168        FIVE_MINUTE_READING(1),
169        BACKFILL(2),
170        IMMEDIATE_MATCH_VALUE(4),
171        CALIBRATION(8),
172        NONE(16)
173
174        ;
175        private int id;
176        CgmDataType(int id) {
177            this.id = id;
178        }
179
180        public static Set<CgmDataType> fromId(int mask) {
181            Set<CgmDataType> items = new TreeSet<>();
182            for (CgmDataType i : values()) {
183                if ((mask & i.getId()) != 0) {
184                    items.add(i);
185                }
186            }
187
188            return items;
189        }
190
191        public int getId() {
192            return id;
193        }
194    }
195
196    public Set<CgmDataType> getCgmDataTypes() {
197        return CgmDataType.fromId(cgmDataTypeRaw);
198    }

219    public enum EgvInfo {
220        FIVE_MINUTE_READING(1),
221        BACKFILL(2),
222        IMMEDIATE_MATCH_VALUE(4),
223        CALIBRATION(8),
224        NO_EGV(16),
225        VALID_TIMESTAMP(32),
226        VALID_EGV_RANGE(64),
227        VALID_ALG_STATE(128),
228        EGV_PROCESSED(256)
229
230        ;
231        private int id;
232        EgvInfo(int id) {
233            this.id = id;
234        }
235
236        public static Set<EgvInfo> fromId(int mask) {
237            Set<EgvInfo> items = new TreeSet<>();
238            for (EgvInfo i : values()) {
239                if ((mask & i.getId()) != 0) {
240                    items.add(i);
241                }
242            }
243
244            return items;
245        }
246
247        public int getId() {
248            return id;
249        }
250    }
